readable.content: A girl in a red polka dot bikini is jumping off a sand dune . A girl with a bikini plays in the dunes . A little girl in a pink bathing suit jumps up on a sand dune at the beach . A young girl in a bikini jumping on the beach . A young girl in a pink bikini jumps into the air on a sandy beach by the ocean , as two other children play in the sand .
